PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773493903
OL,3,CUS eases Russian oil sanctions as Iran
OL,4,Cthreatens to keep Strait of Hormuz
OL,5,Cclosed
OL,7,FOn the war front, the US said it is
OL,8,Flaunching an investigation into an
OL,9,Fincident over Iraq that led to a
OL,10,Frefuelling plane crashing.
OL,12,FThe cause of the crash is not known,
OL,13,Fbut the other plane that was involved
OL,14,Fin the collision was able to land
OL,15,Fsafely.
OL,17,FUS Central Command said it was not
OL,18,Fcaused by enemy or friendly fire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
