OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe fate of the six servicemembers on
OL,13,Fboard is currently unknown, and a
OL,14,Frescue operation is underway.
OL,16,FThe conflict showed no signs of
OL,17,Fslowing down on Friday, with Trump
OL,18,Fissuing a new threat saying, "Watch
OL,19,Fwhat happens to these deranged
OL,20,Fscumbags today."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
