OL,3,CUS eases Russian oil sanctions as Iran
OL,4,Cthreatens to keep Strait of Hormuz
OL,5,Cclosed
OL,7,FHe said it was a "great honour" to be
OL,8,Fkilling the Iranian regime after it
OL,9,Fhad "been killing innocent people all
OL,10,Fover the world for 47 years."
OL,12,FIsrael said it had launched 200
OL,13,Fstrikes on Iran on Friday morning, as
OL,14,FIranian retaliation led to two
OL,15,Fforeigners being killed in Oman.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
