OL,5,Cclosed
OL,7,FFrance also confirmed its first
OL,8,Fcasualty overnight on Thursday, with
OL,9,FFrench President Emmanuel Macron
OL,10,Fconfirming Chief Warrant Officer
OL,11,FArnaud Frion had been killed by a
OL,12,Fdrone in Iraq.
